I feel that my system is better then the other 3 existing PR's revolving around the same concept (no offence to any of the makers or those PR's in anyway what so ever) because in my opinion at least, my system is simpler and easier to use, but yet advanced enough to get a combination of chat formats and colors applied without using over excessive code, this system is easily expandable (within reason) for any future improvements that Mojang decides to add, and on that note I foresee this system withstanding time and updates quite easily. I think that something as simple as sending a chat message should be 3 basic things: Quick, Easy and Painless.
